      "writtenOn": "2016-06-09T21:48:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There is a ShFinalize function, but I spoke with Frank, and it would appear that the global teardown of EGL (which triggers the teardown of GLES2, which would teardown this) doesn\u0027t happen properly right now. So I guess this just adds to the memory leaks :/",
